# Design wiki (llm-wiki)

Wiki vault: `C:\Users\elifs\Projects\llm-wiki`

When the user asks to **ingest**, **query**, or **lint** the wiki:

1. Read `C:\Users\elifs\Projects\llm-wiki\AGENTS.md` and follow it exactly.
2. Raw sources for this project live in `C:\Users\elifs\Projects\llm-wiki\raw\modernz\`.
3. Never modify `raw/` — only write to `wiki/` and `outputs/` in llm-wiki.
4. Tag ModernZ pages with `modernz` in frontmatter.
5. Use `[[wikilinks]]` for internal references (Obsidian graph view).

## Sync sources from this repo

| Repo | Wiki raw |
|------|----------|
| `README.md` | `raw/modernz/README.md` |
| `docs/*.md` | `raw/modernz/` |
| `extras/README.md` | `raw/modernz/extras-README.md` |
| `extras/mpv-mining/README.md` | `raw/modernz/mpv-mining/README.md` |
| `extras/mpv-mining/YOMITAN-SETUP.md` | `raw/modernz/mpv-mining/YOMITAN-SETUP.md` |
